text: Boris Trajkovski ( ; 25 June 1956 – 26 February 2004) was a Macedonian politician who was the president and Supreme Commander of the Republic of Macedonia from 1999 to 2004. He died in a plane crash. ==Other websites== * Official website of the President of Macedonia * The Boris Trajkovski International Foundation * The Evangelical Methodist Church of Macedonia * Ley Hill Methodist Church website – see their History page Category:1956 births Category:2004 deaths Category:Aviation deaths Category:Presidents of North Macedonia
